::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Reptilica and Bloodystrike walk out of a hallway, in between the door and the 
battle between the Alliance and Stalker. Reptilica quickly pushes a button on 
his wrist comp, a blast door separating the two from the battle.

"Let's go," Reptilica says to his friend, the two exiting the base and 
heading for the new femm's pod.
